BzOQ">Thát Sơn Cố Chủ miếu - 獺山故主廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/author-aojK5yt7X8rTWmkDYWXgEg">Trần Huy Liễn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu%E1%BB%B3-b%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-w7DEiYB3UzHtOCSifKigrQ">Thuỳ bạch - 垂白</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-B%C3%B9i-ng%C5%A9-ph%C3%B3-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Xuy%C3%AAn/poem-lOk7uSNl_EQZY5BBCOSk_g">Tống Bùi ngũ phó Đông Xuyên - 送裴五赴東川</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-Ph%C3%BA/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-L%C3%A2m-l%C6%B0u-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-nguy%E1%BB%87t-%C3%A1m-bi-toan/poem-yY7OrfIIGUOkWeIXAf6EnQ">Vô đề (Lâm lưu đối nguyệt ám bi toan) - 無題（臨流對月暗悲酸）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-Ph%C3%BA/author-NMvfSgcxjBLOFSoPM09B4g">Liễu Phú</a>)<br></div>	</div>
